{"tid":493452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無綫資深藝員江漢昨晚離世 享年78歲","createTime":"2017-12-08T14:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T12:51:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":369,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":152,"replies":[{"pid":"5f288cfb613dafacc8b48a51907a04316aa8378f","tid":493452,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171208/large/1512741215_22dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171208%2Flarge%2F1512741215_22dd.jpg&h=f5ef98f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無綫資深藝員，常被派演富商、父親角色的江漢（原名姜永明），昨晚在療養院離世，享年78歲。妻子王小燕接受《蘋果》電話訪問時證實死訊。<br />\n<br />\n據悉江漢年輕時好杯中物，晚年患有管脈炎，令行動不太方便，早前曾入院，之後轉去療養院。而江漢與太太都是鳳鳳影業公司出身，其妻已通知影聯會江漢叔昨晚走了。<br />\n前無綫藝員梁健平昨晚亦收到江漢叔死訊，他說：「噚日江漢叔個女嘅朋友發短訊通知我，話江漢叔噚晚走咗，但冇講詳情。聽到梗係好唔開心啦，江漢叔係一個大好人，以前試過同佢拍《太極》呢套劇，一齊返大陸成個月，我哋都係住埋同一間房，佢為人好客氣好有禮，知我哋伙食唔係咁好，都自己攞錢出嚟請食飯。」<br />\n江漢叔與妻子王小燕都屬鳳鳳影業公司出身，縱橫影視壇已數十年。童星出身的他，演出逾二百部電影，演過無數劇集。年輕時的江漢高大俊俏，是長城和鳳凰電影的當家小生。1979江漢加入麗的電視開始電視生涯，拍過《武則天》、《劍神》、《至尊無上》等劇，92年轉投無綫至今。<br />\n江漢當演慈父角色，令人印象深刻是《烈火雄心3》飾演古天樂、鄧一君的父親。現實生活中，江漢亦是一位慈父，08年因為愛子心切，誤墮電話騙局，被誘騙20萬元，最終因騙徒被監聽，未有蒙受損失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171208/57558635\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57558635&d=DgJ1U%2FQ4SkTgvWt%2FEKlm%2BzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f6b1b886\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57558635&h=f8c7bbe3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171208/57558635</a>"},{"pid":"9d9d511b987c3026fe7163976c96ce3bb3e32325","tid":493452,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ff0d33842fb561dcd6fcf153237bb250c144ae","tid":493452,"uid":19287,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:06:46.000Z","msg":"烈火雄心1呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293064defa0786022ec806a3874173f01a0b47d4","tid":493452,"uid":20896,"like":9,"dislike":276,"score":-267,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"仲有人睇垃圾cctvb?"},{"pid":"3cd50f0513e2dfed920d0aec3dc69e188aa08487","tid":493452,"uid":32723,"like":547,"dislike":4,"score":543,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有人睇垃圾cctvb?</blockquote><br />\n好演員來架老友"},{"pid":"b0ab44ea93d29055e24ad9cfa3bfaf83bbd165c8","tid":493452,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"呢個真係唔記得有咩代表作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過做忠多"},{"pid":"5ae3779b1c3061a20c768baff15ab282fa86856a","tid":493452,"uid":98386,"like":118,"dislike":2,"score":116,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:16:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個真係唔記得有咩代表作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過做忠多</blockquote><br />\n拍過好多劇 講得出就冇乜 只記得佢做過項梁"},{"pid":"45dc99bd698c714d0fb0decded27f27ebdee29dd","tid":493452,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b179bea5283337f5cda22f342bc9bd30c07ffaa1","tid":493452,"uid":16595,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:24:23.000Z","msg":"細細個成日睇佢，rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea01ff68f9871d01428985956b1b37d011eb56fd","tid":493452,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":172,"score":-170,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:25:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76f1f9fdddcbfbb6005c70c9fcfd054279ec5f68","tid":493452,"uid":46155,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"rip \\丨/<br />\n香港人既演員"