quote><br />\n我都覺佢唔啱場合講野<br />\n<br />\n但唔睇tvb同港獨有咩關係？你都幾癡線</blockquote><br />\n佢咁講唔係無根據，其實係有掛鈎，因為只有港獨撚鍵國撚係深信自己唔睇tvb既同時仲要屌人睇tvb，佢地覺得唔睇就可以幫到港獨，實在係越幫越忙至憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身對港獨無乜感覺既人都喺睇緊tvb某啲好劇例如降魔的果時比呢啲on9喺度嘈生晒而開始覺得港獨撚戇鳩鳩盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個因爲係邊撚到黎，有統計？冇根冇據鳩嗡曬鳩氣啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf9dee97a7b42fc49e0e66d8f60e28de801bd42","tid":493452,"uid":16676,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/612366/xlarge/e493ef099198a8df82df123afa31f231.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F612366%2Fxlarge%2Fe493ef099198a8df82df123afa31f231.jpg&h=65ccc212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/97551/thumbnail/472ce13269e588f93fd0d321cd8a51c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F97551%2Fthumbnail%2F472ce13269e588f93fd0d321cd8a51c8.jpg&h=6994e6d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.tvb.com/ii/34/95737/000009573696_1495527520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.tvb.com%2Fii%2F34%2F95737%2F000009573696_1495527520.jpg&h=8c19e350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飾監獄裡面受賄醫生"},{"pid":"f54202a068c06793a122c9648bf731df17a18ffb","tid":493452,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有人睇垃圾cctvb?</blockquote><br />\n香港人一出世就睇TVB <br />\nTVB 就好似空氣一樣既存在<br />\n冇乜話垃唔垃圾<br />\n<br />\n批評香港人親愛既TVB <br />\n就好似批評湊大中國既中共一樣<br />\n何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ca8ac8fd88815e6e5a3d2c96d7dbdb7e0c9bab","tid":49