d7653222","tid":493452,"uid":33058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前成日係天水圍銀座見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  rip</blockquote><br />\n佢住元朗??<br />\n好少聽藝人會成日入天水圍散心嗰喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢應該住嘉湖掛 （9up)<br />\n細細過 0幾年果陣已經係天瑞/北江見過佢 果陣仲諗條友咁熟既係邊到見過<br />\n睇睇下電視同屋企人講起<br />\n屋企人都係銀座見過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1298c95de425c11ebedd50e6e78cc29a21a33393","tid":493452,"uid":30140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:53:41.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"f77954248eb99f3f06bfb5444b3d3dd9612cbff7","tid":493452,"uid":161766,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有人睇垃圾cctvb?</blockquote><br />\n出少句聲冇人話你啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係呢啲唔開心既事上就咪講啲咁嘅野啦. 積下口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75e01c384bf4ddd2cd5342a8053baebd1816ecd","tid":493452,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:56:11.000Z","msg":"見過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRIP\\|/"},{"pid":"c51e8302028ddc652c4319c692e55d2dc1fb3b4e","tid":493452,"uid":161766,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有人睇垃圾cctvb?</blockquote><br />\n你唔睇就熄撚咗個電視唔好網上周圍講呢句嘢騷擾人啦<br />\n港獨唔係咁搞㗎，真係睇撚到煩，講句「乜仲有人睇」就真係冇人睇啦咩<br />\n返返嚟現實好嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個打rip就真係晒鳩氣喇，你打句rip人地就可以安息咩，呢句真係睇到煩。一有人死就rip</blockquote><br />\n講句rip都係出於心意姐. 正如你比人撞到 人地循例都講返聲sorry姐 其實有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca90084165